entries:
  QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Desc:
    contents:
      - text: "Dalia has been working hard to start an orchard,\nbut garbage keeps appearing in her water\nsource, so her efforts are all for naught.\nWhat sort of "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: vile polluter
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: " would toss his or her\ngarbage away with such indifference?"
  QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "Dalia planted the wildberries she received from\nCalyban and said that it's OK to pick them\nonce they grow in.\n\nWith the source of the water pollution cleared\nup, all that's left to do is wait for the wildberries\nto grow."
  QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Name:
    contents:
      - text: The Mystery Polluter
  QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Step1:
    contents:
      - text: "The water source got polluted with garbage, so\nthe water has become unusable. The cause\nturned out to be a woman throwing melon rinds\naway in the waterway upstream. She says if I\nbring her "
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: "10 wildberries "
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "from the snow-topped\npeaks of the Gerudo Highlands, she'll stop\neating so many melons..."
  QL_Gerudo_Ch_Poison_Step2:
    contents:
      - text: "The water source was polluted with garbage, so\nthe water became unusable. The cause turned\nout to be a woman throwing melon rinds away\nin the waterway upstream. In exchange for 10\nwildberries, she agreed to stop eating melons.\nMaybe the water will clear up now.\n\nI should hurry back and report to Dalia."
